[
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Yes, I said; and you may add that they are only fed, and not paid in addition to their food, like other men; and therefore they cannot, if they would, take a journey of pleasure; they have no money to spend on a mistress or any other luxurious fancy, which, as the world goes, is thought to be happiness; and many other accusations of the same nature might be added.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "You mean to ask, I said, what will be our answer?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Yes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Our potters also might be allowed to repose on couches, and feast by the fireside, passing round the winecup, while their wheel is conveniently at hand, and working at pottery only as much as they like; in this way we might make every class happy-and then, as you imagine, the whole State would be happy.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000007_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000007_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "But do not put this idea into our heads; for, if we listen to you, the husbandman will be no longer a husbandman, the potter will cease to be a potter, and no one will have the character of any distinct class in the State.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000007_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000007_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "But, if so, we mean different things, and he is speaking of something which is not a State.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000007_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000007_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "And therefore we must consider whether in appointing our guardians we would look to their greatest happiness individually, or whether this principle of happiness does not rather reside in the State as a whole.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000007_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000007_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "And thus the whole State will grow up in a noble order, and the several classes will receive the proportion of happiness which nature assigns to them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "I think that you are quite right.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "What may that be?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "What are they?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Wealth, I said, and poverty.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "How do they act?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Certainly not.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Very true.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "And the result will be that he becomes a worse potter?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Certainly not.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "That is evident.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "What evils?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Wealth, I said, and poverty; the one is the parent of luxury and indolence, and the other of meanness and viciousness, and both of discontent.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "How so?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "That is true, he said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "And do you not suppose, Adeimantus, that a single boxer who was perfect in his art would easily be a match for two stout and well to do gentlemen who were not boxers?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Hardly, if they came upon him at once.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000035_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000035_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "What, now, I said, if he were able to run away and then turn and strike at the one who first came up?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000035_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000035_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "And supposing he were to do this several times under the heat of a scorching sun, might he not, being an expert, overturn more than one stout personage?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "And yet rich men probably have a greater superiority in the science and practise of boxing than they have in military qualities.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Likely enough.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000042_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000042_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "That is not likely; and yet there might be a danger to the poor State if the wealth of many States were to be gathered into one.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Why so?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "You ought to speak of other States in the plural number; not one of them is a city, but many cities, as they say in the game.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000046_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000046_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "That is most true, he said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000047_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000047_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "And what, I said, will be the best limit for our rulers to fix when they are considering the size of the State and the amount of territory which they are to include, and beyond which they will not go?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000049_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000049_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "I would allow the State to increase so far as is consistent with unity; that, I think, is the proper limit.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Very good, he said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Here then, I said, is another order which will have to be conveyed to our guardians: Let our city be accounted neither large nor small, but one and self sufficing.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "Yes, he said; that is not so difficult.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3330_170956_000056_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3330/170956/3330_170956_000056_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3330",
        "content": "What may that be?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
